All Implemented Interfaces:
Connector, NIOConnector, Dumpable, LifeCycle
public class NetworkTrafficSelectChannelConnector
extends SelectChannelConnector

A specialized version of SelectChannelConnector that supports NetworkTrafficListeners.

NetworkTrafficListeners can be added and removed dynamically before and after this connector has been started without causing ConcurrentModificationExceptions.
